subject: [ANN] Java Gui Builder - 0.5a released
msgSnippet: Java Gui Builder, an XML based GUI building framework, has released version 0.5a. This release brings a menu implementation, and internal refactorings. You may
messageBody:
Java Gui Builder, an XML based GUI building framework, has released
version 0.5a.

This release brings a menu implementation, and internal refactorings.

You may download this project from the project's home page at
http://jgb.sourceforge.net/

Have a nice day !
